        "timestamp": "2018-05-21 13:35:19.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\n(24 comments)\n\nMisspelling of resource needs to be corrected.\nR-88913 needs to be reworded as well.\n A general observation. Repeating restriction from HOT Spec as requirement in VFNRQTS creates a dependency between VNFRQTS and the HOT Specification. For each new release of the HOT Spec we have to re-validate that none of the requirements have changed (for example optional becomes mandatory in the spec but is a **MAY** in VNFRQTS)",
        "patchset_number": 5
